- **[offers.controller.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Backend/src/controllers/offers.controller.ts)** — Added [cancelOffer](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts#42-48) (sender-only), state machine transitions in [updateOfferStatus](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts#28-37), and [getMyBookings](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts#38-41) with user info JOINs
- **[offers.routes.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Backend/src/routes/offers.routes.ts)** — Registered `PATCH /:id/cancel`, `GET /my-bookings`

### Frontend
- **[bookings.model.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/models/bookings.model.ts)** — New [Booking](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/models/bookings.model.ts#7-21) shape matching the API with [BookingUser](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/models/bookings.model.ts#1-6) sub-interface
- **[offer.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts)** — Added [getMyBookings()](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts#38-41), [cancelOffer()](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/services/offer.service.ts#42-48)
