- **[bookings-history.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/pages/bookings-history/bookings-history.ts)** — Real API data, dynamic stats, all action handlers with optimistic updates
- **[messages.ts](file:///c:/Users/Sleiman/Desktop/staajerne/Frontend/src/app/pages/messages/messages.ts)** — Chat deep-linking via `?conversationId=` query param

## Booking Lifecycle

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Pending: Offer created
    Pending --> Confirmed: Recipient accepts
    Pending --> Declined: Recipient declines
    Pending --> Cancelled: Sender cancels
    Confirmed --> InProgress: Recipient starts
    InProgress --> Completed: Recipient marks done
    Completed --> [*]
```

## Validation
- ✅ User confirmed all functionality working
- ✅ Cancel, accept, decline, start progress, done all update UI instantly
- ✅ Message button opens correct chat conversation
- ✅ Done confirmation modal works correctly
